Package: rdhs
Type: Package
Title: API Client and Data Munging for the Demographic and Health Survey Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("OJ", "Watson", role=c("aut", "cre"),
         email="o.watson15@imperial.ac.uk"),
  person("Jeff", "Eaton", role="aut"))
Maintainer: OJ Watson <o.watson15@imperial.ac.uk>
Description: Provides an API client for the DHS API that allows DHS survey indicators
  to be queried. This allows desired indicators to be easily found and passed onto 
  subsequent functionality within rdhs for downloading datasets and conducting basic
  data munging tasks. 
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
